13:["$","$L14",null,{"slug":"local-seo","locale":"en","content":{"metaTitle":"Local SEO Pricing | Plans from $1,500/mo | KINEXIS","metaDescription":"Local SEO pricing for map pack visibility. GBP, citations, reviews, and location pages from $1,500/mo. Month to month, fixed scope at each tier.","hero":{"label":"Local SEO Pricing","line1":"Map pack pricing","line2":"for businesses that win on proximity.","subtitle":"GBP, citations, reviews, and location pages at fixed scope per tier. Not a watered-down version of full SEO."},"answerBlock":"Local SEO plans start at $1,500 per month for single-location service businesses and scale to $5,000+ for multi-city or franchise operators. Every plan covers Google Business Profile optimization, citation cleanup, review strategy, and location page work. Full-site SEO with content and link building is a separate program — see SEO pricing. Most clients see map pack movement within 30 to 60 days. We work month to month.","tiers":[{"name":"Starter","range":"$$1,500/mo","description":"Single-location local SEO for service businesses in mid-competition markets.","bestFor":"Single-location local SEO for service businesses in mid-competition markets."},{"name":"Growth","range":"$$3,000/mo","description":"Multi-location or competitive market local SEO with full citation and content management.","bestFor":"Multi-location or competitive market local SEO with full citation and content management."},{"name":"Scale","range":"$$5,000+/mo","description":"Franchise or high-competition local SEO across multiple cities and service categories.","bestFor":"Franchise or high-competition local SEO across multiple cities and service categories."}],"tiersSection":{"title":"Local SEO vs. DIY map pack work","subtitle":"What changes when someone owns GBP, citations, and reviews every week.","note":"Pricing covers map pack strategy and optimization. One-time citation cleanup is quoted based on current status. Full-site SEO with content and links is priced separately — see SEO pricing."},"included":["Google Business Profile Optimization","Citation Audit & Cleanup","Location Page Creation","Review Generation Strategy","Competitor Gap Analysis","Weekly Rank Tracking"],"includedSection":{"title":"What's included","subtitle":"Everything you need to dominate local search in your market.","items":[{"title":"Google Business Profile Optimization","description":"Categories, services, photos, posts, and Q&A optimized for searches that drive calls in your market."},{"title":"Citation Audit & Cleanup","description":"Consistent NAP data across 45+ directories so Google trusts your location signals."},{"title":"Location Page Creation","description":"Service area pages with real market context, not keyword-stuffed city-name templates."},{"title":"Review Generation Strategy","description":"A sustainable process for earning genuine reviews that improve map pack position and conversion rate."},{"title":"Competitor Gap Analysis","description":"We identify exactly what your top local competitors are doing better and build a plan to overtake them."},{"title":"Weekly Rank Tracking","description":"Map pack and organic position tracking for your priority local keywords, reported weekly."}]},"comparison":{"title":"Local SEO vs. DIY map pack work","subtitle":"What changes when someone owns GBP, citations, and reviews every week.","layout":"progression","columns":[{"header":"Starter","highlight":false},{"header":"Growth","highlight":true},{"header":"Scale","highlight":false}],"rows":[{"label":"Google Business Profile Optimization","values":["Core","Standard","Advanced"]},{"label":"Citation Audit & Cleanup","values":["Core","Standard","Advanced"]},{"label":"Location Page Creation","values":["Core","Standard","Advanced"]},{"label":"Review Generation Strategy","values":["Core","Standard","Advanced"]},{"label":"Best for","values":["Single-location local SEO for service businesses in mid-competition markets.","Multi-location or competitive market local SEO with full citation and content management.","Franchise or high-competition local SEO across multiple cities and service categories."]},{"label":"Starting investment","values":["$$1,500/mo","$$3,000/mo","$$5,000+/mo"]}]},"faqs":[{"question":"Is there a setup fee?","answer":"Most engagements include onboarding and strategy in month one. We quote it upfront. No surprise charges on the first invoice."},{"question":"Do you require a long-term contract?","answer":"No. Month to month. Results should earn your business, not a contract clause."},{"question":"What affects my price?","answer":"Pricing covers map pack strategy and optimization. One-time citation cleanup is quoted based on current status. Full-site SEO with content and links is priced separately — see SEO pricing."},{"question":"Can I start with a smaller plan and upgrade?","answer":"Yes. Many clients start on Starter and move up once momentum builds. We plan the upgrade path so you are not rebuilding from scratch."},{"question":"How is local SEO different from regular SEO?","answer":"Regular SEO chases rankings on standard search results. Local SEO is built for the map pack: Google Business Profile, citations, reviews, and location pages. If your customers search by city or \"near me,\" you need both, but local is what puts you on the map."},{"question":"How much does local SEO cost?","answer":"Single-location businesses start at $1,500 per month. Multi-location brands scale from $3,000 to $5,000+ based on how many markets you cover and how tight the competition is. We quote after looking at your locations and current visibility."},{"question":"How many Google reviews do I need?","answer":"There is no magic number. In competitive markets, staying in the top three map spots often means 50 to 100+ reviews. We focus on steady monthly volume and thoughtful responses, not a one-time push that fades."},{"question":"Do I need Local SEO or full SEO?","answer":"Start with Local SEO ($1,500/mo entry) if map pack visibility and Google Business Profile are your main gaps. Choose full SEO ($2,500/mo entry) if you need technical site work, content, and link building for broader organic growth. Many local service businesses run both. We recommend the mix on a strategy call."}],"ctaHeadline":"Want a quote for local SEO?","ctaSubtitle":"Tell us your service areas and competition.|We will recommend the right tier and map pack strategy.","ctaLabel":"Get Local SEO Pricing","tierProof":{"result":"327% more emergency calls","client":"Plumbing Co.","href":"/case-studies/plumbing-company-growth","tierName":"Growth","sectionLabel":"tier in practice"}},"serviceHref":"/services/local-seo","serviceLabel":"Local SEO Services","breadcrumbs":[{"name":"Home","url":"/"},{"name":"Services","url":"/services"},{"name":"Local SEO Services","url":"/services/local-seo"},{"name":"Local SEO Pricing"}]}]
